89
00:03:52,719 --> 00:03:53,520
You knew?

90
00:03:53,639 --> 00:03:55,319
I only found out recently myself.

91
00:03:56,000 --> 00:03:58,919
Your mother was
my mother's personal maid in Daliang.

92
00:03:59,159 --> 00:04:02,199
Back then, my mother tried
to escape Father's control.

93
00:04:02,840 --> 00:04:05,080
Your mother helped her flee here.

94
00:04:05,800 --> 00:04:06,599
But in the end...

95
00:04:06,599 --> 00:04:07,080
Go inside!

96
00:04:07,280 --> 00:04:08,800
Mother was captured and taken back.

97
00:04:09,479 --> 00:04:12,360
And your parents died because of it.

98
00:04:13,759 --> 00:04:14,879
