108
00:04:35,759 --> 00:04:37,319
He never saw me as his son.

109
00:04:40,199 --> 00:04:42,000
Why should I consider him my father?

110
00:04:44,319 --> 00:04:45,839
This is our revenge.

111
00:04:56,480 --> 00:04:57,279
This is

112
00:04:58,240 --> 00:04:59,279
