113
00:04:59,959 --> 00:05:01,920
He held off an army for us.

114
00:05:02,279 --> 00:05:04,160
Even dying, he told us not to look back.

115
00:05:07,199 --> 00:05:08,079
This is

116
00:05:09,160 --> 00:05:10,000
